summary: This mod adds remixed Undertale music to Skyrim!
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds remixed Undertale music to Skyrim! Most of it is orchestral, and all faithful to the original tracks. All music belongs to Toby Fox and all the people who's remix I used are listed below:
Rob Platt
Malcolm Robinson Music
Hellkite
Megamerge!
Solair Echoes
JindoMusic
ChrystalChameleon
ChunkyVoice
RetroSpecter
Knight Lautrec
James Wong
kage49
Numixi 0u0
Bulby
Gooseworx
If any of the people I've credited want their remix removed, pm me or leave a comment please. Thanks.

Installation (VERY IMPORTANT!)
This mod requires you install the Personalized Music Mod
I reccomend you install the Personalized Music Mod with a manager like NMM to make it easier.
Once you have done that install my mod and extract it.
After you've done that, put all the folders in the Music folder that Personalized Music makes and enjoy!

Update 1.1:
Added Spider Dance to the fight music
Greatly reduced the file size

Let me know if you have any problems, and if you enjoy the mod consider endorsing!
Thanks,
Workmanabs
